    /(?:###?\s*)?(?:\*\*)?Verdict:?\*?\*?\s*\*?\*?\s*(READY_FOR_MERGE|AC_MET_BUT_NOT_A_PLUS|AC_NOT_MET|NEEDS_VERIFICATION)\*?\*?/i,
